Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be cured of your illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to piece together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's like some unimaginable\Nchange is about to take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me that\Nthey misdiagnosed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you have a malignant tumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you will gradually\Nbecome paralyzed and then die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how am I going to be cured?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not... I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...here to be comforted by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only telling you what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you. Please spare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have to pay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.\NI'll never do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the parking lot at Daikoku wharf!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key to our futures lies there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me some money.\NThat'll settle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want 10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to break you to pieces\Nuntil the girls are satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, Akemi.\NThis is some pervert we've got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo?! What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Ozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please just move away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anything with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.19,0:22:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you! What did you do to Akemi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.65,0:22:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo's... Nagumo's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:22:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.38,0:23:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo died...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I tell ya.\NThis medicine sure stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.68,0:23:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best thing for stings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.02,0:24:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.42,0:24:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is overcoming my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.22,0:24:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.93,0:24:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! That light!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.47,0:24:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.27,0:24:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.82,0:24:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistaking it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.24,0:24:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.49,0:24:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ultra God!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.54,0:25:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.29,0:25:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.13,0:25:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't my fault.\NIt couldn't have been my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.30,0:25:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer... Hurry up and answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.81,0:25:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.27,0:25:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Kuroko!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.57,0:25:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.69,0:26:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.45,0:27:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, no! Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.00,0:27:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Please, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.58,0:27:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.76,0:28:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We're not going to make it! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.50,0:29:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? Where's the Ultra God?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.87,0:29:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.04,0:29:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a real ghostly air remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.33,0:29:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.05,0:29:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We were too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.10,0:29:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.15,0:29:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because you didn't notice sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.61,0:29:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.53,0:29:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, take a look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.36,0:29:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a video camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.78,0:29:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good find.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.78,0:29:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.20,0:29:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a waste of\Ntime coming here, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.04,0:29:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.21,0:30:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.93,0:30:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast is ready, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.68,0:30:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.60,0:30:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and we received a\Ncall from the police earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.44,0:30:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to have found your motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.03,0:30:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you walked home last night,\NI filed a report for a stolen bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.21,0:30:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why isn't there anything\Nabout yesterday in the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.63,0:30:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know for sure that Nagumo was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.97,0:30:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't they found him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.76,0:30:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.35,0:30:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember.\NHow exactly did I get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.48,0:30:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that supposed to\Nbe a dream or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.66,0:31:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yuri? What on earth happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.16,0:31:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not showing up at school like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.28,0:31:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika, I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.87,0:31:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri? What's the matter, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.89,0:31:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.18,0:31:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.94,0:31:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.48,0:31:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo? Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.65,0:31:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, somehow I ended\Nup at Red Brick Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.65,0:31:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Brick Park? What are you\Ndoing there so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.24,0:31:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying to get a hold of you\Nsince last night. Yuri's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.04,0:31:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Yuri is?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.62,0:32:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.63,0:32:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.63,0:32:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I don't know\Nwhat the hell is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.22,0:32:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo shows up at school\Nlike nothing happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.22,0:32:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and not a scratch on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.85,0:32:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.82,0:32:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.78,0:32:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.66,0:32:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell whoever it is I'm not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.41,0:32:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.71,0:32:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.88,0:32:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything all right with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.59,0:32:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.38,0:32:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.84,0:32:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.84,0:32:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to\Nsay at times like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.26,0:32:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.22,0:32:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were\Ngoing to tell him straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.52,0:32:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.35,0:33:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would he have done that to Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.98,0:33:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. I'll tell him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.73,0:33:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you sure? But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.40,0:33:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think a girl can deal with\Nthis sort of thing better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.78,0:33:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Takamine Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.45,0:33:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.33,0:33:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt strangely compelled\Nto answer Ozaki's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.59,0:33:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Nagumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.26,0:33:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.18,0:33:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better come for\Nyour biopsy this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.22,0:33:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki? Hey, Ozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.43,0:33:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time had stopped at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.48,0:33:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I realized everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.27,0:33:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why he had called me. And why he's\Nstaking so much on becoming champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.90,0:33:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo? Nagumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.86,0:33:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki might have cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.41,0:33:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.12,0:33:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.08,0:34:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were at a loss for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.34,0:34:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Mika didn't know\Nwhat to say to Ozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.18,0:34:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we just walked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.18,0:34:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.35,0:34:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was moving in a\Ndirection that I hadn't anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.11,0:34:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.95,0:34:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.49,0:34:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, the tumor\Ndidn't show up on the x-ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.00,0:34:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did a regular\Ncheck-up just last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.46,0:34:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it's a fault with the MRI.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.54,0:34:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be cured of your illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.92,0:34:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel, Ozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.13,0:34:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.51,0:35:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my memory's been\Nhazy since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.76,0:35:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.81,0:35:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that does happen\Nin the case of brain tumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.02,0:35:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's do a blood test.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.31,0:35:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it, but you may\Nhave been completely cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.07,0:35:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And next week we'll do another MRI.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.91,0:35:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could've happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.24,0:35:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I really have been cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.83,0:35:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was what Akemi said really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.80,0:35:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Some kind of amateur porn?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.72,0:35:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.76,0:35:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it kind of exciting to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.39,0:35:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.60,0:35:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Boss! It's him! It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.35,0:35:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.53,0:36:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it was\Nworth looking into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.37,0:36:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, how can you just\Nleave that demi-beast alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.45,0:36:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amanojaku is no ordinary demi-beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.54,0:36:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.54,0:36:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't we be in more trouble\Nif he gets to the Ultra God first?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.30,0:36:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seigenki...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.89,0:36:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't obey me...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.68,0:36:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm not going to let you off...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.02,0:36:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just because you're my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.90,0:36:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Suikakuju has fought\Nwith him many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.57,0:36:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he can't seem to ever\Nsettle it once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.95,0:36:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not capable as you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.70,0:36:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.20,0:36:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your order is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.87,0:36:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be sure to defeat him one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.92,0:36:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.26,0:37:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a report of an unusual\Nincident in Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.97,0:37:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was an incident last night that I\Nthought I should report to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.85,0:37:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the malignant brain tumor\Nhas disappeared without surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.11,0:37:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not another case of fraud\Nlike in France recently, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.28,0:37:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.36,0:37:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the data I sent you, I've also\Nincluded results of his blood test.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.07,0:37:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His genetic make-up seems to be\Ngetting closer to what we think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.62,0:37:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have it checked out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.54,0:37:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.38,0:37:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.89,0:37:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.14,0:37:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't confirm it with him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.73,0:37:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.99,0:38:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.49,0:38:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one closest to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.24,0:38:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know him better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.20,0:38:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't at all aware of the\Nsuffering he was going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.88,0:38:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.84,0:38:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only thinking about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.38,0:38:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not... That's not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.18,0:38:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?\NWhy does it have to be Ozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.48,0:38:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't I supposed to be cured? Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.88,0:39:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.19,0:39:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.98,0:39:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki's somehow regained\Nhis strength and has gotten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.78,0:39:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he seems to be hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.95,0:39:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Ozaki be eliminated\Nfrom the tournament here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.20,0:39:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homma of Kaisei College\Nhas ample energy left.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.75,0:39:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki has just gotten\Nup but he still looks shaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.96,0:39:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can he really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.25,0:39:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.46,0:39:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.98,0:39:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.07,0:40:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Homma?\NYou'll lose points for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.81,0:40:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.85,0:40:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.27,0:40:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are the arrangements?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.61,0:40:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokakuryu is on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.69,0:40:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.69,0:41:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.15,0:41:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worse than an insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.99,0:41:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I think I wanted\Nit to be you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.04,0:41:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should apologize, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.96,0:41:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't even aware of\Nwhat was going on with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.63,0:41:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed as a manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.01,0:41:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll support you as\Nbest as I can until you're cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.09,0:41:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it'll be the three of us.\NJust like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.64,0:41:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.64,0:42:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's been going\Non with me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.56,0:42:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see things that aren't there and\NI'm haunted by hallucinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.98,0:42:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not sure if what's\Nhappening is real or a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.41,0:42:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.12,0:42:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! Look at the way\Nyou won your fight today!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.79,0:42:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.25,0:42:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I really win?! Tell me how I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.09,0:42:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even remember\Nhow it played out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.97,0:42:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to just forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.10,0:42:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.85,0:42:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't.\NAnd please don't talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.61,0:42:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.36,0:42:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Ozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.78,0:42:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please! Let me be close to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.00,0:43:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.42,0:43:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.69,0:43:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a blackout? That scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.11,0:43:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Ozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.15,0:43:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.03,0:43:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.66,0:43:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.17,0:43:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.17,0:43:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hallucination?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.71,0:43:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.13,0:43:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.21,0:43:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is reality. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.30,0:44:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm taking your girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.85,0:44:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think the Ultra God's woman\Nwould be such a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.06,0:44:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.48,0:44:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.48,0:44:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.73,0:44:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ultra God has a Lolita fetish?\NThese tits aren't even fully developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.37,0:44:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.87,0:44:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.66,0:44:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Dokakuryu,\Nwill take care of your woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.17,0:44:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.63,0:44:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks like you know a\Nthing or two about this after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.10,0:44:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.89,0:44:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel to be ravaged\Nin front of the one you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.11,0:44:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! You feel better the\Nmore you hear him writhe!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.28,0:45:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.49,0:45:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better hurry up, Ultra God. Or\Nyour woman will be of no use to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.25,0:45:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ultra God.\NIf you want your woman back...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.13,0:45:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you will have to\Nreveal your true powers!